1.5.0
- Upon start, check if a valid download mirror is set, otherwise use first from list.
- Fix action bar text color.
- Test on older Android versions, 5 and up.

1.6.0
- Improve "Materialization": paddings\margins, typography.
- Add more media to display for files. Screenshots, external reviews, videos, etc.
- Update app navigation.
- Replace reliance on /idgames API with custom API.
- Render reviews in RecyclerView for performance.
- Allow Idgames entries to be serialized so that parsing responses is not necessary when reloading views.
